490
00:31:43,430 --> 00:31:46,770
Kurasa aku mengalami gangguan pencernaan.

491
00:31:46,869 --> 00:31:49,139
Mungkin makanku terlalu cepat.

492
00:31:53,579 --> 00:31:55,250
Aku tak bohong, Bu.

493
00:31:55,250 --> 00:31:56,710
Bukan kau yang kumaksud.

494
00:31:57,919 --> 00:31:59,750
Siapa yang butuh obat?

495
00:32:00,119 --> 00:32:02,520
Aigoo, aku pastinya.

496
00:32:02,520 --> 00:32:05,119
Aku merasa sakit perut.

497
00:32:05,119 --> 00:32:08,030
Jika kau minum obat yang salah,
