534
00:35:35,069 --> 00:35:36,869
Mungkin dia masih tidur.

535
00:35:38,110 --> 00:35:39,170
Aku juga mau tidur.

536
00:35:39,170 --> 00:35:41,039
Ibu akan terus menelepon Seung Woo.

537
00:35:41,039 --> 00:35:43,809
Beri tahu Ibu jika kalian
mendengar sesuatu darinya.

538
00:35:46,909 --> 00:35:47,950
Kang Bok Su.

539
00:35:48,950 --> 00:35:51,550
Pekerjaan sukarela itu penting,
tapi jangan telat masuk kelas.

540
00:35:54,819 --> 00:35:56,719
Kang Bok Su, kau mau bilang sesuatu?

541
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:05,170
Jangan berbuat masalah.

542
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:07,069
Terutama Kang Bok Su.

543
00:36:13,170 --> 00:36:15,580
(Yoon Seung Woo)

544
00:36:22,450 --> 00:36:24,150
Dua-duanya tidak diangkat.

545
00:36:25,050 --> 00:36:27,920
