tidak bolos sekolah tanpa alasan.

546
00:36:28,319 --> 00:36:29,390
Iya.

547
00:36:29,589 --> 00:36:31,129
Dia memang tak pernah
memperhatikan di kelas,...

548
00:36:31,129 --> 00:36:32,860
...tapi dia tidak pernah melewatkan kelas.

549
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:37,300
Dia dulu jadi siswa terbaik saat SMP.

550
00:36:38,029 --> 00:36:39,200
Seung Woo?

551
00:36:39,469 --> 00:36:41,499
Mungkin Anda salah.

552
00:36:41,499 --> 00:36:43,240
Dia menjadi yang terbawah di Kelas Wildflower.

553
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:46,170
Aku sudah melihatnya,...

554
00:36:46,170 --> 00:36:49,309
...tapi karena kau bilang
dia tak pernah melewatkan kelas...

555
00:36:49,309 --> 00:36:51,779
... tanyakan ke
teman-temannya di mana dia biasanya.

556
00:36:51,909 --> 00:36:52,979
Ya.

557
00:37:00,589 --> 00:37:01,859
Katakan, Son Soo Jeong.

558
00:37:03,460 --> 00:37:05,830
Kenapa ada gambarmu di ruang kantor Oh Se Ho?

559
00:37:05,830 --> 00:37:08,159
