562
00:37:15,870 --> 00:37:18,070
Ini diibaratkan dengan seseorang.

563
00:37:20,710 --> 00:37:21,779
Aigoo, dasar!

564
00:37:28,919 --> 00:37:30,020
Pak.

565
00:37:31,219 --> 00:37:32,320
Kang Bok Su.

566
00:37:33,549 --> 00:37:36,859
