567
00:37:43,729 --> 00:37:46,200
Katamu mau tanggung jawab.

568
00:37:46,200 --> 00:37:48,299
Ibu Son Soo Jeong.

569
00:37:48,799 --> 00:37:52,239
Kau tak memantau pekerjaan sukarela Kang Bok Su?

570
00:37:52,239 --> 00:37:54,140
Maaf.

571
00:37:54,140 --> 00:37:56,440
Aku akan mengeringkan
pakaian Anda.../ Sudah kering, kok.

572
00:38:00,049 --> 00:38:03,080
Bagaimana bisa kau dimarahi
cuma karena kau belum mengeringkan pel?

573
00:38:04,690 --> 00:38:06,419
Kau kenapa sebenarnya?

574
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:11,289
Hei, Kang Bok Su.
Kau mau bilang sesuatu?

575
00:38:13,789 --> 00:38:14,859
Hei.

576
00:38:28,580 --> 00:38:31,750
Ah, diriku ini kenapa?

577
00:38:34,219 --> 00:38:37,690
Kendalikan dirimu.
