635
00:42:05,659 --> 00:42:06,890
Tapi, Sajang-nim.

636
00:42:07,459 --> 00:42:09,159
Sajang.

637
00:42:09,529 --> 00:42:12,169
Jika orang-orang tahu kau
mempekerjakan anak di bawah umur,...

638
00:42:12,169 --> 00:42:13,870
